▶ Patient Under Investigation(PUI)

 



 3. Within 14 days

 

 

 



  Fever or respiratory symptoms after visiting Wuhan city

→

Pneumonia with radiological evidence after visiting China

Expanded



[Figure 1] Changes on the case definition
 
○ In addition, the first confirmed patient has been treated for pneumonia, and the second confirmed case is in stable condition. These two patients have contacts of 45 with four PUIs and 75 with seven PUIs respectively, but all of PUIs were diagnosed as negative and released from isolation as of today.
* Link to further information in Korean : https://www.cdc.go.kr/board/board.es?mid=a20501000000&bid=0015&act=view&list_no=365874&tag=&nPage=1


